HEADWORD: Revocatory
<hw>Rev"o**ca*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>revocatorius</ets>: cf. F. <ets>r⟦eacute⟧vocatoire</ets>.]</ety>
